    DateTimeParserCommons

    ParserCommons interface contains all the constants and methods that are shared by two or more parser classes.

    DeleteCategoryParser
    The DeleteCategoryParser class provides methods for deleting a category.

    EditParser

    The FloatParser takes in a "float" or "editToFloat" command input and returns a Command object.

    The MarkParser class takes in a "mark" command input and returns a Command object.

    TagParser
    TagParser class takes in a string of task IDs and returns an array list of task IDs.

    UnmarkParser
